Double click a software instrument / [[MIDI]] ''region''



[[File:GBregion.png]]


In the editor that appears select the notes you want to quantize then select an option from the '''Align to''' menu.

Choose the quantization value you want.


[[File:Gb quantize.png]]



You can quantize other MIDI data by clicking the View menu and choosing any of the available options.



